metadata.description:
The 1st Beauty and the Room #1

Beauty are celebrating in her bedroom before Christmas night with tiger and her lovely friends.

She take this beautiful occasion as an opportunity to remind you how much you mean to her. She pray to give you whatever you wish for.

I want to wish you a Merry Christmas from bottom of my heart ❤️
